                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- row 2 -->
                    <div class="hidden lg:block col-start-5 col-span-1 font-medium">02.</div>
                    <div class="col-start-6 col-span-5">
                        <h3 class="font-medium pb-4">Defining the business goal and strategic direction</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-500 font-medium">
                            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Soluta dolorem quos adipisci accusantium perferendis velit dolor, corrupti nam esse sunt maxime qui praesentium nihil ipsum minus obcaecati laudantium assumenda sed pariatur dolorum quidem. Accusantium rem voluptates consequatur placeat, eius dolores!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <div class="container py-48">
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:justify-between lg:items-center gap-8 lg:gap-0 py-12">
                    <h2 class="text-6xl lg:text-9xl font-bold capitalize">
                        services
                    </h2>
                    <div>
                        <ContactButton />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <ServicesComponent />
            </div>
        </section>

        <AboutSection 
            hasButton={false}
            number="1" 
            p1="As a web designer and art director I help companies and organisations around the world connect with their audience and grow their business." 
            p2=""/>

        <PortfolioItem
            client="Starbucks"
